{"tid":737541,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原諒定唔原諒","createTime":"2018-07-11T02:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T02:57:02.000Z","uid":179582,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"af18406392addc804dd0c83e21a811afe698b3f6","tid":737541,"uid":179582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:20:14.000Z","msg":"純FF題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n某日你遇到一個同你夾得埋，而且又互相對對方有意思嘅人<br />\n<br />\n但係你之後發現佢曾經做過啲你點都接受唔到嘅嘢（個個唔同所以你自己代入返你接受唔到嘅事），所以你就冇繼續呢段關係<br />\n<br />\n對方好sad，過咗一段時間佢唔知點樣整咗部時光機出嚟搵你，請你返到佢未做果樣嘢嗰陣同佢一齊<br />\n<br />\n唔討論可唔可行啊，究竟過去嘅佢會唔會一樣對你有意思呢啲，純粹討論你會唔會take呢個offer<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：去，既然未做又點責怪佢呢<br />\n<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔去，能夠做得出呢啲事嘅人可以好得去邊，就算佢此刻未做出嚟，咪預我"},{"pid":"0f44da4498d3f4d86bc4d86f573dd1c3e1600252","tid":737541,"uid":151691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:22:52.000Z","msg":"做完之後去改變等於冇做？<br />\n你知佢喺過去嘅時空做過已經不了"},{"pid":"97ffa999857f85fa856a3cc36101e24b71c20a45","tid":737541,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"識整時光機嘅老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd429413e77d580929b6003446481b5d7b66d7b4","tid":737541,"uid":193407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:35:57.000Z","msg":"唔去 等距後悔一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a2e6e35352902acf34fe54fe5433855ddb42b2","tid":737541,"uid":31001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"唔去 人要為做過既野負責"},{"pid":"ce5d9c5b2caa0a179b15237e2354f75fe064853b","tid":737541,"uid":179582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69a2e6e35352902acf34fe54fe5433855ddb42b2","tid":737541,"uid":31001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T